      <title>贸易紧张局势加剧 中国将对欧盟猪肉进口展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/china-to-probe-eu-pork-imports-as-trade-tensions-rise-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已对欧盟进口猪肉发起反倾销调查。据中国商务部声明，调查于周一开始。中国是欧盟最大的猪肉海外市场。彭博社的 Oliver Crook 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/china-to-probe-eu-pork-imports-as-trade-tensions-rise-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行调查显示零售商认为最糟糕的时期已经过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/riksbank-survey-shows-retailers-believe-worst-is-behind-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行对企业的调查显示，瑞典商业领域的经济形势仍然弱于正常水平，但各行各业都明显希望形势将在六个月内有所改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/riksbank-survey-shows-retailers-believe-worst-is-behind-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在家办公倡导者 Stellantis 呼吁工程师重返办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/stellantis-champion-of-home-work-asks-engineers-back-to-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 公司已让其汽车工程师重返办公室，此举推翻了首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 在疫情爆发后为削减公司开支而采取的提倡在家办公的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/stellantis-champion-of-home-work-asks-engineers-back-to-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典卡尔诺夫电厂股价因财团撤回竞标而创下历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/sweden-s-karnov-falls-most-on-record-after-consortium-pulls-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典法律服务提供商 Karnov Group AB 在斯德哥尔摩的股价暴跌 22%，此前两家美国投资公司因股东反对而撤回了对该公司的收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/sweden-s-karnov-falls-most-on-record-after-consortium-pulls-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:42:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对欧盟进口猪肉启动反倾销调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-launches-anti-dumping-probe-on-imports-of-eu-pork</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对从欧盟进口的猪肉发起反倾销调查，这是一项针对性较强的措施，也是北京和布鲁塞尔之间贸易紧张局势的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-launches-anti-dumping-probe-on-imports-of-eu-pork</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
